m(B) \geq 1
B = \bigcap\limits_{t=1}^{\infty} \bigcup\limits_{n \geq t}^{\infty}A_n
 x\in B \Leftrightarrow \forall t \in \mathbb N \text{ } \exists n \in \mathbb{N}: n \geq t \text{ and } x \in A_n \Leftrightarrow x \in \bigcap_{t=1}^{\infty} \bigcup_{n \geq t}^{\infty}A_n
C_t = \bigcup\limits_{n \geq t}^{\infty}A_n
C_{t+1} \subset C_t
m(B) \geq 1
1 \leq m(A_n) \forall n \in \mathbb{N} \Rightarrow 1 \leq m(C_t) \forall t \in \mathbb{N}\Rightarrow 1 \leq \lim_{t \to \infty}m(C_t) \overset{(*)}{=}m(\bigcap\limits_{t=1}^{\infty} C_t )= m(B)
